---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="The Archive | XXIV ARCHIVE">

<section class="hero">

    <div class="hero-content">

        <p>XXIV ARCHIVE</p>

        <h1>
            A Living Museum<br>
            of Sound,<br>
            Memory & Time.
        </h1>

    </div>

</section>

<section class="section">

    <div class="container">

        <p class="label">THE PHILOSOPHY</p>

        <h2>Music deserves to be preserved.</h2>

        <p>

Most releases disappear into endless playlists.

XXIV ARCHIVE was created to preserve music differently.

Every project becomes an exhibition.

Every exhibition is supported by photography, written reflections, publications and visual storytelling.

Instead of chasing moments, the archive preserves them.

        </p>

    </div>

</section>

<section class="section">

    <div class="container">

        <p class="label">THE ARTIST</p>

        <h2>Behind the Archive.</h2>

        <p>

I don't separate music from memory.

Every photograph, every production decision and every lyric belongs to the same story.

XXIV ARCHIVE is where those stories are preserved.

Not as content.

As exhibitions.

        </p>

    </div>

</section>

<section class="section">

    <div class="container">

        <p class="label">THE MISSION</p>

        <h2>Building a permanent collection.</h2>

        <p>

Every future release expands the archive.

Each exhibition becomes another room inside the museum.

The collection is never finished.

It simply continues to grow.

        </p>

    </div>

</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>

.hero{

height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;

}

.hero-content{

max-width:1000px;

}

.hero p{

letter-spacing:10px;
color:#B89D68;
font-size:.8rem;

}

.hero h1{

font-size:6.5rem;
font-weight:300;
line-height:1.15;
margin-top:30px;

}

.section{

padding:180px 8%;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;

}

.container{

max-width:900px;

}

.label{

letter-spacing:8px;
color:#B89D68;
margin-bottom:25px;

}

.container h2{

font-size:3.5rem;
font-weight:300;
margin-bottom:35px;

}

.container p{

font-size:1.2rem;
line-height:2.1;
color:#b5b5b5;

}

@media(max-width:900px){

.hero h1{

font-size:3.5rem;

}

.container h2{

font-size:2.3rem;

}

.section{

padding:120px 8%;

}

}

</style>